Timecode;;48;;68;;R;;A production company begins casting for its next feature, and an up-and-coming actress named Rose (Salma Hayek) tries to manipulate her filmmaker boyfriend, Alex, into giving her a screen test. Alex's wife, Emma (Saffron Burrows), knows about the affair and is considering divorce, while Rose's girlfriend secretly spies on her and attempts to sabotage the relationship. The four storylines in the film were each shot in one take and are shown simultaneously, each taking up a quarter of the screen.;;Drama;;Mike Figgis;;2000;;Xander Berkeley,Golden Brooks,Saffron Burrows,Viveka Davis,Richard Edson,Aimee Graham,Salma Hayek,Glenne Headly,Andrew Heckler,Holly Hunter,Danny Huston,Daphna Kastner,Patrick Kearney,Elizabeth Low,Kyle MacLachlan,Mia Maestro,Leslie Mann,Suzy Nakamura,Alessandro Nivola,Zuleikha Robinson;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/timecode